OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thu 23 Apr to Sat 2 May
OL,6,FHigh pressure is likely to be centred
OL,7,Fto the north of the UK through much of
OL,8,Fthis period. Overall, many places will
OL,9,Fprobably be largely dry with clear or
OL,10,Fsunny periods. There is a chance of
OL,11,Fsome rain or showers at times in the
OL,12,Ffar southwest and northeast, perhaps
OL,13,Fturning wintry in parts of Scotland.
OL,14,FWind may be strong at times around
OL,15,Fcoasts, mainly in the southwest and
OL,16,Fnortheast. Temperatures will probably
OL,17,Fbe near normal or slightly above for
OL,18,Fmany, but with a risk of colder
OL,19,Fconditions affecting the north at
OL,20,Ftimes.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
